{"tid":886334,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣不倫床戲瘋傳　「男上女下」遭狂吻","createTime":"2018-11-02T04:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T23:46:23.000Z","uid":9573,"like":7,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"64e6288bb46e305b0e445fbf65dbf102032c22aa","tid":886334,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:35:02.000Z","msg":"30歲日本女星新垣結衣2016年憑藉電視劇《月薪嬌妻》躍升「國民老婆」，近日她演出新作《無法成為野獸的我們》，和松田龍平共譜戀曲，2人進度超前，最新一集中甚至出現激吻床戲，讓不少把新垣結衣當作「老婆」的網友崩潰心碎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/09/28/1563720-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F1563720-XXL.jpg&h=42863737&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新垣結衣演出《無法成為野獸的我們》。<br />\n<br />\n《無法成為野獸的我們》昨日播出第4集，飾演女強人「深海晶」的新垣結衣和好好先生「根元恒星」松田龍平因緣際會下在酒吧相遇，時常互吐心聲，進而從「酒友」變「床友」，發展出一段屬於成人世界的戀愛。新垣結衣罕見突破尺度演出床戲，為了報復出軌男友，不僅主動要求和松田龍平一夜情，還不停嬌喊：「你鬍子好刺」、「要親嗎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/11/01/1620665-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F11%2F01%2F1620665-XXL.jpg&h=8ca17c35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲新垣結衣和松田龍平劇中是酒友。<br />\n<br />\n不過請諸位「老公」放寬心，劇情中，松田龍平在前戲時，就因為不勝酒力睡著，同時艾朗藍斯在陣中已被邊緣化，過去三輪英超僅後備披甲，遭新垣結衣虧是「做到一半睡著的男人」。這突破尺度的演出片段，在網路上被瘋狂轉發，不少「老公」仍無法接受新垣結衣的床戲，心碎表示：「看得我心如刀割」、「拜託告訴我，這是替身」、「松田龍平放開我老婆」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.caixin.com/2015-12-16/1450232017942178_266_177.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.caixin.com%2F2015-12-16%2F1450232017942178_266_177.jpg&h=de6ce74e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼新垣結衣、松田龍平在劇中發展一夜情。<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.afinance.cn/new/UploadFiles_2266/201604/20160407153807618.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afinance.cn%2Fnew%2FUploadFiles_2266%2F201604%2F20160407153807618.jpg&h=adf0bd56&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b7e102570c5e04ad1dd4fda7f7fff57908cf8f67","tid":886334,"uid":7837,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:38:25.000Z","msg":"同時艾朗藍斯在陣中已被邊緣化，過去三輪英超僅後備披甲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da49510ccdcb99875cc2bfbc3efc179e4078e0b6","tid":886334,"uid":54455,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:41:33.000Z","msg":"Ok負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8bb9b208991ca34a5ab964423bd1efa64657961","tid":886334,"uid":26451,"like":12,"dislike":14,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c2654e3a8047070c62aba9a2333c06860d6cb75f","tid":886334,"uid":3535,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:51:21.000Z","msg":"那個了哦"},{"pid":"2805198ed9dfd19ed073c249bac595492b3b5846","tid":886334,"uid":27851,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8bb9b208991ca34a5ab964423bd1efa64657961","tid":886334,"uid":26451,"like":12,"dislike":14,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:52:07.000Z","msg":"師兄呢度我頂住。。快d走。。。"},{"pid":"b1474784162f41a02cd43dff3d323af093fc844b","tid":886334,"uid":33864,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"f8bb9b208991ca34a5ab964423bd1efa64657961","tid":886334,"uid":26451,"like":12,"dislike":14,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:32:08.000Z","msg":"出嚟隻抽"},{"pid":"e9be7d92b6a66b9a295b9e2971e4f8a941589e89","tid":886334,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f8bb9b208991ca34a5ab964423bd1efa64657961","tid":886334,"uid":26451,"like":12,"dislike":14,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:50:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T05:34:00.000Z","msg":"你講乜野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9aad02a23a21815d663382b58622b4f45d79bf7","tid":886334,"uid":48083,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2